{"tid":432988,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"承諾不拆民主牆物品 浸大校長錢大康：不限制討論港獨","createTime":"2017-10-12T04:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T05:01:58.000Z","uid":48083,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"abd93b7ad8ff96deb323cfbb44566dd2dbba6e86","tid":432988,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:02:17.000Z","msg":"本港多間大學爆發港獨宣傳品爭議，10間大學校長上月中發表聯合聲明反對港獨，又譴責「濫用言論自由的行為」。浸會大學學生會透露，上周跟校長錢大康會面，表達學生對聲明內容的關注，錢大康在席間承諾，校方未來不會推出任何政策，限制校內有關港獨的討論，亦不會拆除民主牆上物品。<br />\n<br />\n多間大學的民主牆上月起出現各樣港獨宣傳品，其中，浸會大學不曾拆除任何宣傳品，浸大校方曾發表聲明，指民主牆屬學生會管理，校方不作干涉。對此，浸大學生會外務副幹事長麥筠瑋表示，校長錢大康應學生會邀請、上周會面時，再次重申民主牆全權由學生會負責，因此校方不會拆除民主牆上任何內容。<br />\n麥筠瑋表示，雖然該校民主牆未受干預，但10間大學校長高調發出聲明反港獨，學生會及同學均憂慮大學內部將存在審查，暗地裡限制教職員討論或研究港獨議題。對此，他引述校長錢大康會上承諾，校方未來不會推出限制討論港獨的政策。<br />\n浸大學生會亦不滿「大學校長聲明」下款以10間大學作署名，而非相關校長用個人名義聯署，麥筠瑋認為，聲明內容僅代表各名校長的個人想法，並不代表大學立場，聯署方法並不恰當。錢大康承諾往後遇上同類情況，會考慮以個人名義聯署，或在使用「浸會大學」名義作出聲明前，事先跟學生會討論，防止學生聲音被忽略。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171011/57319949\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171011%2F57319949&d=6mBMeeO8Haym%2FeubmfjcP2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=7748d0ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171011%2F57319949&h=440268fe\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171011/57319949</a>"},{"pid":"014070d44b872629fc821cff22fb71cec3e140cc","tid":432988,"uid":91721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523a8b2b9a6042f757f4dcb90ecdfc359270a8a9","tid":432988,"uid":83097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:04:24.000Z","msg":"呢D咪有骨氣囉"},{"pid":"34b94acf2d3026e2d7e5085d9628275b8df363e2","tid":432988,"uid":47359,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:04:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">poly就日日拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"987280c1630cdd3112600bd4ca43508da5c9a7e9","tid":432988,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:05:24.000Z","msg":"講人話"},{"pid":"7552852657f2327bd52ee86e4706b3d4b313847b","tid":432988,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:06:23.000Z","msg":"唔知可以頂到幾耐<br />\n<br />\n希望堅持到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b06e697526ba483e72d06326c372827a6bef77","tid":432988,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:06:23.000Z","msg":"唔知可以頂到幾耐<br />\n<br />\n希望堅持到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6587c1ec8ff2b9d4c1a214ea98685a5b4617be","tid":432988,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:21:07.000Z","msg":"真大學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dfcde28742b7f2828b744ad2cd5b6a3344720b7","tid":432988,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}